    <title type="html">Thunderbird 131.0</title>
    <author>
      <name>Thunderbird</name>
      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/131.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2024-10-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2024-10-01T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Event and Task reminders contained incorrect sleep duration units</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash when using return receipt with OWL add-on</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash on startup</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Opening an EML file with a 'mailto:' link did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Message window froze after clicking 'mailto:' link containing child elements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Saving an EML file that was opened from a file did not work</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Delete confirmation could appear twice when using shift+delete</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Mark All Read" on Quick Filter results marked all emails in folder as read</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Collapsed POP3 account folder was expanded after emptying trash on exit</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Messages deleted from a cross-folder search view could not be undeleted</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Mark Folder Read" on a cross-folder search marked all underlying folders read</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Repairing local folders caused messages in folder to temporarily disappear</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Repairing an IMAP folder resulted in incorrect total and unread message counts</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Performance could be degraded when using cards view with tags</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unable to "Decrypt and Open" an attached OpenPGP key file</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unable to open/view attached OpenPGP encrypted messages</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Stored draft messages were not encrypted when recipients were not specified</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Quick Filter reset sort type in threaded views sorted by "Order Received" ascending</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Changing a saved draft's send identity did not prompt to save the modified message</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Subject could disappear when replying to a message saved in an EML file</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>"Attach this image to the message" checkbox not checked when inserting image</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Display names for SMTP servers could be incorrectly formatted as a date</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Some users were unable to log in to Microsoft 365</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>OAuth2 authentication method was not available when adding SMTP server</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird crashed when run from flatpak installation</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Matrix end-to-end encryption tab in account settings could show for XMPP account</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Participant and message were not populated when user left the room using XMPP</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Flatpak release notes URL was incorrect</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unable to subscribe to .ics calendars in some situations</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Visual and UX improvements</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/known-vulnerabilities/thunderbird/#thunderbird131">Security fixes</a></p>
          
        </li>
      
    
    </ul>
  
  

<p>As always, you’re encouraged to <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/questions/new/thunderbird">tell us what you think</a>, or <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/">file a bug in Bugzilla</a></p>
<style> li p { display: inline; } </style>
      ]]>
    </content>
